rows.label: tlk42350122_03_msg0001
rows.name:
You know, I used to live
in a town called Echell.

rows.label: tlk42350122_03_msg0002
rows.name:
There, I fell in love with a
certain girl at first sight.

rows.label: tlk42350122_03_msg0003
rows.name:
She was the lord's daughter, you see.
She was so refined, a true lady.

rows.label: tlk42350122_03_msg0004
rows.name:
If I wasn't a Phonex, I would have
proposed to her without a doubt.

rows.label: tlk42350122_03_msg0005
rows.name:
But before I knew it, she
was gone... The whole
mansion had disappeared.

rows.label: tlk42350122_03_msg0006
rows.name:
I was so shocked at the time. I
hope I can see her again someday.
